      finals, weighted scores, and GPA.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- TOOLS -->
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Tools</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/grade-calculator">Grade Calculator</a></li>
      <li><a href="/final-exam-calculator">Final Exam Calculator</a></li>
      <li><a href="/weighted-grade-calculator">Weighted Grade Calculator</a></li>
      <li><a href="/gpa-calculator">GPA Calculator</a></li>
      <li>
        <a href="/what-grade-do-i-need-calculator">
          What Grade Do I Need Calculator
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- GUIDES (SEO TRAFFIC) -->
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Guides</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="/how-to-calculate-your-grade">
          How to Calculate Your Grade (Step-by-Step Guide)
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
  <a href="/what-grade-do-i-need-to-pass-a-class">
    What Grade Do I Need to Pass a Class?
  </a>
</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- EXTRA CONTEXT FOR SEO -->
  <div class="card">
    <h2>About These Tools</h2>
    <p>
      This site provides easy-to-use calculators to help students track their
      academic performance. Whether you're calculating your current average,
      figuring out what you need on a final exam, or tracking your GPA, these
      tools are designed to give you fast and accurate answers.
    </p>

    <p class="muted">
      More tools coming next: cumulative GPA calculator, semester GPA tracker,
      and advanced grade projections.
    </p>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>